<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> The nomination shall include a cultural project of European dimension, based principally on cultural cooperation, in accordance with the objectives and action provided for by Article 151 of the Treaty. </inglise>
