<inglise> The submission shall specify how the nominated city intends: </inglise>
<eesti> &Uuml;lesseadmisel m&auml;&auml;ratletakse, kuidas kandidaatlinn kavatseb </eesti>
<inglise> - to highlight artistic movements and styles shared by Europeans which it has inspired or to which it has made a significant contribution, </inglise>
